She's wearing a blue sports bra and black-to-purple ombre shorts. The bathroom has a modern design with bright lighting and multiple mirrors creating an infinity effect.

Text overlay on the video suggests starting with stretching. The post includes hashtags related to lower body workouts, gym workouts, and women's fitness.

The image is an Instagram post featuring a motivational quote by Jim Rohn: "Big achievements come one small advantage at a time, one step at a time, one day at a time." The post also includes a caption emphasizing consistency and not letting failures define you.
The image shows a woman (camid_fit) performing squats with a barbell in a gym setting. The post details her lower body workout routine.
